Package eu.wauz.wauzcore.oneblock

This package contains classes for the one-block gamemode.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OneBlock
    The one infinite block from the one-block gamemode.
    OneBlockProgression
    The progrss of a player in the one-block gamemode.
    OneChest
    A reward chest of a phase of the one-block gamemode.
    OneChestItem
    An item that can be contained inside a reward chest of the one-block gamemode.
    OnePhase
    A phase of the one-block gamemode.
    OnePhaseLevel
    A level of a phase of the one-block gamemode.
    OnePlotCalculator
    Used for calculating positions of one-block plots.
    OnePlotManager
    Used for managing one-block plots.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OneChestType
    The types of chests, that can spawn in the one-block gamemode.
